Scenario summary
----------------
1. There are 2 Accounts. 
2. Coinbase mined block 1,2 - so balance of coinbase is 10 ether
3. Create 1 trasaction, Sends 1 ether to other.
4. Coinbase mined block 3 with transaction - so balances are 10 + (5-1) ether, 1 ether each.
